{"tid":2025223,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美軍軍機今早以呼號「happy day」經巴士海峽飛往南海","createTime":"2020-05-20T06:01:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T07:05:04.000Z","uid":28765,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7d578a141d2166cd4f1f68f60820ff8769351f4d","tid":2025223,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T06:01:56.000Z","msg":"〔記者蔡宗憲／屏東報導〕台灣南端巴士海峽近年常有各式美國軍機掠過，特殊呼號常成為軍事迷討論焦點，今天適逢蔡英文總統520就職，典禮進行期間竟出現「happy day」呼號，疑有偷偷祝福含意，令不少記錄下的軍事迷莞爾。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/05/20/3171321_1_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F05%2F20%2F3171321_1_1.jpg&h=7c93b8b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n記錄下的軍事迷老許說，這架隸屬沖繩嘉手納基地的美國海軍P-3C反潛機，今天上午10點左右，以高度22500英呎通過巴士海峽往南海飛去，呼號竟是「happy day」。<br />\n<br />\n老許表示，透過飛機追蹤網站「Plane Finder」，近期常能發現美國軍機掠過巴士海峽，各式各樣的呼號也是民主國家的展現，這次選在520剛好使用「happy day」當呼號，確實引人聯想「空中送上遙遠祝福」的含意。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3171321\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3171321&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krPcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=96fc5455\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3171321&h=bd97d6fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3171321</a>"},{"pid":"5669cb194803b9a6fe883726c2a697526653ab2e","tid":2025223,"uid":195894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T06:06:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4651e253cb3faac27c51f42bdbc8675ddbfd13cf","tid":2025223,"uid":271199,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T06:17:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />台灣no.1"},{"pid":"24b3e134f6639fd7a7ef7f8a4dcf28f9e8e1b232","tid":2025223,"uid":167597,"like":0,"dislik